citation.case_name: King v. Crosby, Secretary, Florida Department of Corrections

html:
537 U.S. 1230

KING
v.
CROSBY, SECRETARY, FLORIDA DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS.

No. 02-9230 (02A720).

Supreme Court of United States.

February 26, 2003.

1

CERTIORARI TO THE UNITED STATES COURT OF APPEALS FOR THE ELEVENTH CIRCUIT.

2

C. A. 11th Cir. Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to JUSTICE KENNEDY, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Certiorari denied.
